{"tid":1524000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【831太子恐襲】9月1號機場見","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:19:39.000Z","uid":78255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02913c1cb935ac7c81a6877d000999ebcbcf3568","tid":1524000,"uid":78255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月1號入機場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月1號入機場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月1號入機場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n每個星期日都入機場<br />\n<br />\n搭地鐵唔好再俾黨鐵賺，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全世界都要跳閘chok閘彈閘都唔準再俾錢！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nkeep住洗版洗到全版都係9月1日入機場！"},{"pid":"801ea2e0647fc6f6e5a2f530ef1eada7601921f3","tid":1524000,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXnY1hQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXnY1hQ.jpg&h=abafa30f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7160a4c8fa7f2caa4aa22e59e8e67286ad4641bd","tid":1524000,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<b